definition:
Descendants from Rapha, who lived at the time of United Monarchy, first mentioned at 2Sa.21.16; 
 father of: Goliath (H1555), Ishbi-benob (H3430), Saph (H5593), Lahmi (H3902), huge_man (H4060A); also translated "giant";
Group of ra.pah (רָפָה "Rapha" H7497A)
  giants, Rephaim
 old tribe of giants
